[tool.poetry.group.test.dependencies]

[[tool.poetry.source]]
name = "artifactory.intuit"
url = "https://artifact.intuit.com/artifactory/api/pypi/pypi-intuit/simple/"
priority = "primary"

[tool.black]
line-length = 88
target-version = ['py311']

[tool.isort]
profile = "black"

[tool.pytest.ini_options]
log_level = "DEBUG"
addopts = "-n auto --cov=app --cov-report= --color=yes --ignore=fullflows --ignore=docs --maxfail=50 --tb=short --dist=loadgroup --timeout=300 --timeout-method=thread"
asyncio_default_fixture_loop_scope = "function"
markers = ["integration: mark a test as a integration test.",
          "unit: mark a test as a unit test.",]
pythonpath = [
    "app",
]
 testpaths = [
     "tests/",
     "app/test/",
 ]
asyncio_mode = "auto"
[tool.coverage.run]
source = ["app"]
parallel = true
concurrency = ["multiprocessing", "thread"]
sigterm = true
omit = [
    "*/tests/*",
    "*/test_*",
    "*/__pycache__/*",
    "*/.tox/*",
    "*/htmlcov/*",
    "*/coverage/*",
    "*/fullflows/*",
    "*/docs/*",
    "*/venv/*",
    "*/.venv/*"
]

[tool.coverage.report]
precision = 2
show_missing = true
skip_covered = false
exclude_lines = [
    "pragma: no cover",
    "def __repr__",
    "raise AssertionError",
    "raise NotImplementedError",
    "if __name__ == .__main__.:",
    "if TYPE_CHECKING:",
    "@abstractmethod"
]

[tool.coverage.paths]
source = [
    "app",
    ".tox/*/lib/python*/site-packages/app"
]

[build-system]
requires = ["poetry-core>=1.0.0"]
build-backend = "poetry.core.masonry.api"

[tox]
envlist =
    lint,
    python3.11,

[testenv]
passenv = APP_ENV
skip_install = true
allowlist_externals = *poetry
# Poetry may not be in the path (e.g. if running in Jenkins)
# In that case, assume the location is in the POETRY environment variable
setenv =
    POETRY = {env:POETRY:poetry}
commands_pre = {env:POETRY} install
commands = 
    {env:POETRY} run coverage erase
    {env:POETRY} run pytest --cov=app --cov-fail-under=30 --cov-report html --cov-report term --cov-report xml:coverage/coverage.xml --color=yes --ignore=fullflows --ignore=docs --maxfail=50 --tb=short 

[testenv:lint]
commands =
    {env:POETRY} run isort --version
    {env:POETRY} run isort --check-only --df .
    {env:POETRY} run black --version
    {env:POETRY} run black --check --diff .
    {env:POETRY} run mypy --version
    ; {env:POETRY} run mypy .

[report]
